'''Hannibus''' was a [[dragon rider]], who served [[Zaros]] near the end of the [[Second Age]]. When Zaros was betrayed by his general [[Zamorak]], some of the dragon riders remained loyal to Zaros, while others joined Zamorak's rebellion. Hannibus, however tried to remain neutral, by not declaring loyalty to either faction.  {{CiteNPC|npc=Ablenkian|loc=Ablenkian's escape|quote=I did not betray our lord like Apropos did, nor did I cowardly sit on the fence like Hannibus.|name=Ablenkian}}

